rating_comment: It's right beside the main road, so the accessibility is good but so is the noise. the apartment was not tidy, it was rather small and had a weird smell. there are very few amenities inside the apartment, and the surrounding is also dirty. but if you're here for the location, then yes, it's recommended. otherwise it's not recommended at all.

rating_comment: Overall my stying experience was good . Only suggestion is that please arrange something for drinking waters as we have buy and carry big jars during our stay . As this property doesn’t have any WiFi facility so we had faced too much network issue as this room is totally inside the complex building. Even in day time we had to use electric lights .

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · March 2024,  · Stayed with kids
rating_comment:
My family had a great experience staying in M.A.'s place for 20 days. The apartment building is very convenient to most of the common needs - restaurants, groceries, embassies, hospitals, pharmacies, and banks etc. Throughout our tenure of stay, M.A. was very responsive, flexible, and overall a wonderful host. Besides, M.A.'s staff Mr. Delwar was very welcoming and helpful! We will definitely be back again. 100% recommended!
Thank you, M.A.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · February 2024,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: It was good a budget place with all basic aminities

We had a great stay and this place felt like home, almost free of mosquitoes, has full time security and access to elevators. Host was very responsive and had all the necessary information when asked. From this location its easy to get transportation to airport or other part of Dhaka.
